<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Gopi Portfolio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Color variables */
    :root {
      --gold-light:  #fff4d6;
      --gold:        #D4AF37;
      --gold-dark:   #A7851C;
      --dark:        #2a2a2a;
      --white:       #ffffff;
    }

    /* Reset box-sizing and spacing */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    /* Set custom cursor for page */
    html, body {
      cursor: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='63' height='63'><defs><radialGradient id='g'><stop offset='0%' stop-color='%23FFD700'/><stop offset='100%' stop-color='%23FFA500'/></radialGradient></defs><circle cx='31.5' cy='31.5' r='28' fill='url(%23g)'/></svg>") 31 31, auto;
    }

    body {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background: var(--gold-light);
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Scroll progress bar styling */
    #scroll-progress {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 4px;
      background: transparent;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    #scroll-progress-bar {
      height: 100%; width: 0%;
      background: var(--gold);
      transition: width 0.1s ease-out;
    }

    /* Layout for left and right panels */
    .left, .right { width: 50%; position: relative; }

    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media(max-width: 800px) {
      body { flex-direction: column; }
      .left, .right { width: 100%; }
    }

    /* Left panel styles */
    .left { overflow: hidden; }
    .blob { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100%; min-width: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .hello { position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 0; width: 80%; transform: rotate(-12deg); pointer-events: none; }
    .portrait { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 5%; height: 95%; width: auto; max-width: 90%; }

    @media(max-width: 800px) {
      .hello { top: 5%; width: 120%; }
      .portrait { left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); height: 60%; }
    }

    /* Right panel styles */
    .right {
      padding: 10vw;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--gold-light);
    }
    .right h2 {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--gold-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px var(--gold);
    }
    .right p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Call-to-Action Button */
    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75em 1.5em;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 4px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .cta::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: -100%;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      transform: skewX(-30deg);
      transition: left 0.5s;
    }
    .cta:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .cta:hover::after { left: 200%; }

    @media(max-width: 800px) {
      .right { padding: 5vw; }
      .right p { max-width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Scroll Progress Indicator -->
  <div id="scroll-progress">
    <div id="scroll-progress-bar"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Left side with images -->
  <div class="left">
    <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/gopichakradhar/assets/blob11.png" alt="Blob Background" class="blob">
    <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/gopichakradhar/assets/hello.svg" alt="Hello Text" class="hello">
    <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/gopichakradhar/assets/super-removebg-preview.png" alt="Portrait Image" class="portrait">
  </div>

  <!-- Right side with textual content -->
  <div class="right">
    <h2>ABOUT</h2>
    <p>
      Mandepudi Gopi Chakradhar, better known as Gopi, discovered his passion for technology and coding during his school days in Khammam.
    </p>
    <p>
      He pursued Computer Science at IIITDM Kurnool, enhancing skills in full-stack development, machine learning, and practical projects.
    </p>
    <a href="https://gopi-chakradhar.vercel.app/" class="cta">View Portfolio</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
